**NASA Open Science Training**
NASA Open Science Training is a free learning platform that helps researchers, students, and professionals understand and apply open science principles, including open data, open-source software, and collaborative research practices. It offers self-paced courses such as Open Science Essentials and Open Science 101, along with certificates and digital badges upon completion.
Link: https://science.nasa.gov/open-science/

